&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to work as a SPA advisor in the Single Point of Referral in Retford. Part of the Notts HC organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be part of a motivated, forward thinking team. Who provide an effective and efficient communication and liaison service across the full range of services, determining, signposting and navigating service users and staff to other services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working closely with multiple other services and organisations and supporting the Notts HC services and teams to ensure equality of access across the full range of services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact Lucy Kingston, Single Point of Referral advisor on either lucy.kingston@nottshc.nhs.uk or 01777 274422&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
